trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Windows.Shell.ThumbButtonInfo"></xref> objects that are associated with a <xref href="System.Windows.Window"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en samling av <xref href="System.Windows.Shell.ThumbButtonInfo"> </xref> objekter som er knyttet til en <xref href="System.Windows.Window"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: ThumbButtonInfoCollection is a strongly-typed <xref:System.Windows.FreezableCollection%601> that is used to support declarations in [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xaml-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: ThumbButtonInfoCollection er en strongly-typed <xref:System.Windows.FreezableCollection%601>som brukes til å støtte deklareringer i [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xaml-md.md)].</xref:System.Windows.FreezableCollection%601>

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[win7](~/add/includes/win7-md.md)] shell allows a maximum of seven buttons in the taskbar preview.
trans-unit.target: Den [!INCLUDE[win7](~/add/includes/win7-md.md)] grensesnittet tillater maksimalt sju knapper i forhåndsvisningen oppgavelinjen.

trans-unit.source: If more than seven <xref:System.Windows.Shell.ThumbButtonInfo> objects are added to the ThumbButtonInfoCollection, the additional objects are treated as overflow.
trans-unit.target: Hvis mer enn sju <xref:System.Windows.Shell.ThumbButtonInfo>objekter er lagt til i ThumbButtonInfoCollection flere objekter behandles som overflyt.</xref:System.Windows.Shell.ThumbButtonInfo>

trans-unit.source: When a button is <xref:System.Windows.Visibility>, it does not have any visible elements and no space is reserved for it.
trans-unit.target: Når en knapp er <xref:System.Windows.Visibility>den ikke har noen synlige elementer og ingen mellomrom er reservert for det.</xref:System.Windows.Visibility>

trans-unit.source: In this case, additional buttons from the ThumbButtonInfoCollection overflow are displayed.
trans-unit.target: I dette tilfellet vises flere knapper fra ThumbButtonInfoCollection overflyt.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Shell.ThumbButtonInfoCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Shell.ThumbButtonInfoCollection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny forekomst av samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The new instance of the collection.
